@drgiraffe_books The first book series that helps children cope with illness.
.
Explaining an illness to a child, whether common or serious, is no easy feat. It’s something every parent must do, but knowing what to say and how to say it, can be a huge challenge. Often, they simply don’t have the medical knowledge needed to explain a disease and provide much-needed comfort. This is where Dr Giraffe comes in.
.
Books available Chicken pox, Cleft-pallet & lip book and Leucemia in 4 different languages (EN, NL, FR & PT): .
www.drgiraffe.com
.

JUST BORN!! @drgiraffe_books It has been 5 years on the making! Like any self-initiated projet needs a lot of believing so I want to thank my friends and family who stuck by me. ❤️ It is just the beginning:  Three books (chicken pox, cleft pallet & lip and leucemia) in 4 different languages has been released. I hope this projects can give comfort of the difficult times parents go through.
.
Special thanks to Jayshree Viswanathan @mizvis , Stefan Liute and Marjan van Mourik to be part of it together!
.
You can find more www.drgiraffe.com
.
